OL,3,CConcern over future of Jersey's most
OL,4,Cpopular sport as profits plummet
OL,6,FOrganisers of most popular sports
OL,7,Fevent say it needs to be restructured
OL,8,Fto secure its future.
OL,10,FHorse racing has dominated the Channel
OL,11,FIslands' sporting scene since 1832
OL,12,Fwith Princess Anne even taking part in
OL,13,Fa Jersey race in 1988.
OL,15,FHowever, recent times have been
OL,16,Ftougher with not hosting a race since
OL,17,F2020.
