OL,3,CConcern over future of Jersey's most
OL,4,Cpopular sport as profits plummet
OL,6,FNow Jersey Race Club tell ITV News
OL,7,Fthat a combination of falling ticket
OL,8,Fsales and a lack of sponsorship is
OL,9,Fcause for concern.
OL,11,FChair Jim Cantle explains his view on
OL,12,Fthe decline in attendances: "I just
OL,13,Fthink there are other things to do, it
OL,14,Fis the lack of interest in racing on
OL,15,Fthe island which I can never
OL,16,Funderstand.
OL,18,F"We do a lot of marketing but we just
OL,19,Fneed to try and get more people
OL,20,Finvolved.
