OL,3,CConcern over future of Jersey's most
OL,4,Cpopular sport as profits plummet
OL,6,F"We're shocked by some of the sponsors
OL,7,Fwho have been with us for the last
OL,8,Fthree years but times have changed and
OL,9,Fso have the economics of it all,
OL,10,Fobviously the first thing they're
OL,11,Fgoing to pull in the budget is
OL,12,Fsponsoring horse racing."
OL,14,FIt costs #600,000 to run a series of
OL,15,Frace meets each year, 15% more than
OL,16,Ffive years ago, and with attendances
OL,17,Fdropping from 6,000 two decades ago to
OL,18,Fas little as 1,000 per race now, there
OL,19,Fis growing concern about where the
OL,20,Flost money will come from.
