OL,3,CConcern over future of Jersey's most
OL,4,Cpopular sport as profits plummet
OL,6,FThe club is currently just about
OL,7,Fbreaking even.
OL,9,FStaffing has been cut from its heyday
OL,10,Fwith Glyn Mitchell now one of only two
OL,11,Fgroundsmen left at the club.
OL,13,FHe says: "I stopped my own business to
OL,14,Fdo this so it was quite a big
OL,15,Fknockback but to be honest, I am so
OL,16,Fpassionate about this site and racing
OL,17,Fin general. But It needs an uplift."
