OL,3,CConcern over future of Jersey's most
OL,4,Cpopular sport as profits plummet
OL,6,FJersey's government supported horse
OL,7,Fracing with a financial grant during
OL,8,Fthe Covid pandemic but has not
OL,9,Finvested in the sport since.
OL,11,FSports Minister, Constable Andy Jehan,
OL,12,Fsays: "All sports are struggling for
OL,13,Ffinancial support during this time,
OL,14,Fwe've not seen anything to do with
OL,15,Ftheir books to see how sustainable
OL,16,Fthey are and at this time we are not
OL,17,Foffering grants to organisations.
OL,19,F"But if they have problems we are
OL,20,Fhappy to talk to them again."
